<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      
      .container {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }
      
      .header p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }
      
      .content {
        padding: 40px;
      }
      
      .status {
        background: #d4edda;
        border: 2px solid #28a745;
        color: #155724;
        padding: 15px 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      
      .status-icon {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        background: #28a745;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      
      .section {
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }
      
      .section h2 {
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        border-bottom: 3px solid #667eea;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
      }
      
      .api-list {
        list-style: none;
      }
      
      .api-item {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        padding: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      
      .api-item:hover {
        transform: translateX(5px);
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      
      .api-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      
      .method {
        padding: 5px 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }
      
      .method.get {
        background: #28a745;
        color: white;
      }
      
      .method.post {
        background: #007bff;
        color: white;
      }
      
      .method.put {
        background: #ffc107;
        color: #333;
      }
      
      .method.delete {
        background: #dc3545;
        color: white;
      }
      
      .endpoint {
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #495057;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      
      .description {
        color: #6c757d;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      
      .example {
        background: #2d3748;
        color: #68d391;
        padding: 12px 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        overflow-x: auto;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      
      .example-label {
        color: #a0aec0;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }
      
      .info-box {
        background: #e7f3ff;
        border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
        padding: 15px 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      
      .info-box h3 {
        color: #1976D2;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      
      .info-box p {
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      
      .footer {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #6c757d;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      
      .footer a {
        color: #667eea;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      
      .footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .header h1 {
          font-size: 1.8rem;
        }
        
        .content {
          padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .api-header {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 10px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>üè† <%= title %></h1>
        <p>RESTful API for Real Estate Management System</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <div class="status">
          <div class="status-icon">‚úì</div>
          <span>API is running successfully!</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
          <h2>üìã Available API Endpoints</h2>
          
          <ul class="api-list">
            <li class="api-item">
              <div class="api-header">
                <span class="method get">GET</span>
                <span class="endpoint">/housing</span>
              </div>
              <p class="description">
                Retrieve all housing properties. Returns an array of all properties in the database.
              </p>
              <div class="example-label">Example:</div>
              <div class="example">
                curl http://localhost:3000/housing
              </div>
            </li>
            
            <li class="api-item">
              <div class="api-header">
                <span class="method get">GET</span>
                <span class="endpoint">/housing/:id</span>
              </div>
              <p class="description">
                Retrieve a specific housing property by its ID. Replace <code>:id</code> with the MongoDB ObjectId.
              </p>
              <div class="example-label">Example:</div>
              <div class="example">
                curl http://localhost:3000/housing/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
              </div>
            </li>
            
            <li class="api-item">
              <div class="api-header">
                <span class="method get">GET</span>
                <span class="endpoint">/housing?type={type}</span>
              </div>
              <p class="description">
                Filter housing properties by type. Supported types: <strong>rumah</strong>, <strong>apartemen</strong>, <strong>villa</strong>.
              </p>
              <div class="example-label">Example:</div>
              <div class="example">
                curl http://localhost:3000/housing?type=rumah
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
          <div class="info-box">
            <h3>üì¶ Response Format</h3>
            <p>
              All endpoints return JSON format. Success responses contain the requested data, 
              while error responses include a <code>message</code> field with error details.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="info-box" style="margin-top: 15px;">
            <h3>üîó Integration</h3>
            <p>
              This API is designed to work with the <strong>Griya MDP Angular Application</strong>. 
              Make sure to enable CORS if accessing from a different domain.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
          <h2>üìä Data Model</h2>
          <div class="example" style="margin-top: 15px;">
{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Griya Asri Residence",
  "location": "Jakarta Selatan",
  "price": 850000000,
  "bedrooms": 3,
  "bathrooms": 2,
  "area": 120,
  "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/...",
  "rating": 4.5,
  "status": "Available",
  "type": "rumah",
  "description": "Modern minimalist housing...",
  "postedDays": 2
}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          Built with ‚ù§Ô∏è using Express.js & MongoDB | 
          <a href="https://github.com/Web-Programming/spa-with-angular-nurrachmat-nr" target="_blank">
            View on GitHub
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
